    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Enemy is growing with you</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you pick an upgrade, you also pick an upgrade for your enemies, adding an extra layer of strategy around your builds. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you really want to give an enemy more attack speed or is it better to make them more tanky? Your choice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hell or Heaven? Both?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Depending on your choices you can easily turn this game into a bullet heaven, but make some risky decisions and you will quickly find yourself in a bullet hell. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlockables and Difficulties</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A quest system to give you more choices for your builds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Prestige with each run to make your ship stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 main difficulties to beat. The Royal Difficulty will infinitely scale up, so you never run out of a challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Not sold yet? Try the demo!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the demo version to get a taste of Novi Blaster. Get the full game to access the progression system and harder difficulties. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[The Demo will be available soon!]</p>",
